蓮蓬摘下留空柄，
把向船前探水深。', 'parsed', 'cnnt-auto', '{"queue_id":"CN-TR-00556","source_record_id":"CN-NT-CAT-00139","alias_record_ids":["CN-NT-CAT-00139"],"batch":"song-yuan-ming-auto","source_url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/%E9%87%87%E8%93%AE%E6%9B%B2_(%E5%BE%90%E7%85%A7)","review_status":"auto-extracted","review_reasons":[]}'),
    ('candidate-song-5f90-7167', 0, '妾薄命', NULL, '五言律詩', 5, '初與君相知，
便欲腸肺傾。
