始悟非真情。
妾情不可收，
悔思淚盈盈。', 'parsed', 'cnnt-auto', '{"queue_id":"CN-TR-00557","source_record_id":"CN-NT-CAT-00140","alias_record_ids":["CN-NT-CAT-00140"],"batch":"song-yuan-ming-auto","source_url":"https://zh.wikisource.org/wiki/%E5%A6%BE%E8%96%84%E5%91%BD_(%E5%BE%90%E7%85%A7)","review_status":"auto-extracted","review_reasons":[]}'),
    ('candidate-song-5f90-7167', 0, '舟中', NULL, '五言律詩', 5, '秋氣清如水，
推篷夜不眠。
